    <div class="container">
        <div class="section">
            <h2>Community Guidelines</h2>
            <p>Our community is built on the pillars of respect, collaboration, and growth. To maintain a positive environment, we expect every member to adhere to the following guidelines:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Respect and Inclusivity:</strong> Treat everyone with dignity, regardless of their background or experience level. Harassment or discrimination of any kind will not be tolerated.</li>
                <li><strong>Constructive Feedback:</strong> Provide feedback that is constructive, respectful, and aimed at improving ideas or projects.</li>
                <li><strong>Transparency:</strong> Communicate openly and honestly. Misleading others or providing false information is strictly prohibited.</li>
                <li><strong>Collaboration:</strong> Support fellow members by sharing knowledge, ideas, and experiences. Teamwork is at the heart of our community.</li>
                <li><strong>Confidentiality:</strong> Respect the privacy and confidentiality of discussions, especially when handling sensitive startup information.</li>
                <li><strong>Compliance:</strong> Adhere to all legal requirements, intellectual property rights, and company policies while engaging with the community.</li>
            </ul>
            <p>By being part of our community, you’re not just an observer — you’re a contributor to a network that thrives on mutual growth and shared success.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
